1. To build the docker image, in the current directory
docker build ./ -t wezuo/ortmodule-sccl-pytorch-cuda-cudnn-devel:image_version

3. To push the image to docker hub
docker push wezuo/ortmodule-sccl-pytorch-cuda-cudnn-devel:image_version

4. Version control: v[x].[y]
   y: for minor revision
   x: for major update
   Everytime one of the following component in the package changes, please increase x by 1. Everytime if bug is fixed in one of the component but not updating the version, please increase y by 1.
      * ORTModule
      * SCCL_interpreter
      * SCCL_synthesizer
      * pytorch
      * cuda
      * cudnn
   Everytime when update the image, please update the ReleaseNote (in this folder) for detailed documentation of the versions of each component.
